    <item>
      <title>Vodafone Idea 未来两年寻求 18 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/vodafone-idea-seeks-1-8-billion-of-loans-in-next-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，沃达丰创意有限公司 (Vodafone Idea Ltd.) 正在与贷方就未来两年内总计 1500 亿卢比（18 亿美元）的贷款进行谈判，亿万富翁库马尔·曼加拉姆·比拉 (Kumar Mangalam Birla) 领导的无线运营商正寻求扭转其不盈利的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/vodafone-idea-seeks-1-8-billion-of-loans-in-next-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:37:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼旗舰店因一次性充电而利润下滑38%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/adani-flagship-s-profit-slips-38-bogged-down-by-one-time-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼企业有限公司 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 的季度利润下降了 38%，受到孟买机场一次性收费的影响，而亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的集团计划投资 1000 亿美元用于绿色能源转型和扩大业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/adani-flagship-s-profit-slips-38-bogged-down-by-one-time-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:35:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飞利浦睡眠呼吸暂停交易为未来的癌症索赔留下了空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/philips-sleep-apnea-deal-leaves-opening-for-future-cancer-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皇家飞利浦公司 (Royal Philips NV) 以 11 亿美元解决美国针对 550 万台被召回的睡眠呼吸暂停设备提起的诉讼，该和解仅解决了当前案件，并没有为未来可能因这些机器引发的癌症索赔留出资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/philips-sleep-apnea-deal-leaves-opening-for-future-cancer-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:04:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币的现状一点也不强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-05-02/crypto-is-anything-but-strong-right-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业支持者表示，他们已经从上次崩盘中吸取了教训，但监管机构需要更快地采取行动，以保护新一波主流投资者免受同样的老故事的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-05-02/crypto-is-anything-but-strong-right-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
